    "source_text": "在2020年，我們成功獲得監管機搆批復，將上海分公司改建為中國內地首家外資獨資人身保險子公司。於2021年\n3月，我們已獲得中國銀行保險監督委員會批復，准予在四川省開業。四川省是中國內地以國內生產總值計的\n第六大省份，以人口計為第四大省，為友邦保險帶來重大的長期增長機遇。",
    "current_translation": "In 2020, we successfully obtained regulatory approval to restructure our Shanghai branch into Mainland China's first wholly foreign-owned life insurance subsidiary. In March 2021, we received approval from the China Banking and Insurance Regulatory Commission to commence operations in Sichuan Province. As the sixth largest province in Mainland China by GDP and the fourth largest by population, Sichuan Province presents significant long-term growth opportunities for AIA."
  },
